dsDescriptionValue.value: 47 subjects performed a Posner type task in an event-related design twice, once under placebo, once under nicotine. Data is published as Breckel TP, Giessing C, Gieseler A, Querbach S, Reuter M, Thiel CM: Nicotinic modulation of attention-related neural activity differentiates polymorphisms of DRD2 and CHRNA4 receptor genes. PlosOne 2015.
